---
title: Saucy Lemon Pepper Chicken with Charred Corn Garlic Rice
description: If you haven’t tried our peri peri sauce then you’re missing out. We’re here to rectify that. Drizzle the sauce over a zesty
pepper chicken and enjoy how the flavours soak into the sweetcorn rice. You’re peri peri experience awaits!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
